<DIV1 TYPE="title page">
<PB REF="017450_0002_0FA11E99F264C990">
<P>A SERMON PREACHED BEFORE HIS EXCELLENCY JOHN HANCOCK, <ABBR>ESQ</ABBR> GOVERNOUR; HIS HONOR THOMAS CUSHING, <ABBR>ESQ</ABBR> LIEUTENANT-GOVERNOR; THE HONORABLE THE COUNCIL, AND THE HONORABLE THE SENATE, AND HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE COMMONWEALTH OF MASSACHUSETTS, MAY 29, 1782, Being the Day of General Election.</P>
<P>BY ZABDIEL ADAMS, A. M. PASTOR OF THE CHURCH IN LUNENBURG.</P>
<P>COMMONWEALTH OF MASSACHUSETTS: PRINTED BY T. &amp; J. FLEET AND J. GILL.</P>
</DIV1>
