<OPENER><DATELINE>In the Hou&s;e of REPRESENTATIVES, <DATE>MAY 29, 1782.</DATE></DATELINE></OPENER>
<P>On Motion,
<HI>ORDERED,</HI> That <HI>John Rowe,</HI> <ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> Capt. <HI>Jo&s;iah Stearns,</HI> and <HI>William Vans,</HI> <ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> be a Committee to wait on the Rev. <HI>Zabdiel Adams,</HI> and thank him in the Name of the Hou&s;e for the Sermon delivered by him this Day, and to reque&s;t of him a Copy for the Pre&s;s.</P>
